Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.76,0:00:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.59,0:00:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's have a snowball fight, Onikiri-kun, Kotetsu-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, Nanami-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The kimono, you received from Kamehime-sama, will get soaked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry~!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a contract between you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I will turn you into a human,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but on the condition,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.40,0:01:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that you will marry that woman for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.07,0:01:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I will grant your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.68,0:01:28.94,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That voice is constantly echoing in my head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that woman's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.61,0:01:32.16,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's it talking about?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe! The shrine gate crumbled!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.34,0:01:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-dono's power, that held the shrine together, seems to be fading!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.92,0:01:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman's name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,She is to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.57,0:01:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,...my lifelong partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:08.34,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fade(2000,2000){\pos(180,275)}The God\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\h                                leaps into the Past
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.58,0:02:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.36,0:02:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.67,0:02:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...help me to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did you remember... Tomoe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.42,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...about Yukiji-san...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-sama, here are the peach pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe, you'll be alright once you take these-!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That sort of thing won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.08,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Move and stay over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Somebody help!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe will... Tomoe will die!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you remember, Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let anyone touch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.26,0:03:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax and have a good sleep, Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.66,0:03:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.08,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe is inside this mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How joyous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage-sama has returned home after 20 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A feast! Prepare a feast! Prepare the sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, will-o-wisps!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.24,0:04:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-chan is my only master.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikage-sama returning home is none of my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.04,0:04:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected from the Yonomori shrine's refined sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... you are Mizuki-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Also Nanami-san, thank you for being the Mikage shrine's land god for all this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what were those marks?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.14,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe's heart has frozen right now and he's sleeping inside the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,But he might not last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those marks are a curse that will kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.90,0:05:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not some sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They have been engraved upon him as a price for an ancient agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe probably has... only 7 days more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,500 years ago, when I first met Tomoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the shadow of death was already on his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,As I thought. These marks are from a curse cast by a wicked fallen god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.72,0:05:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You made some kind of contract with a fallen god, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I vowed to spend my entire life with a human woman I loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that woman died, I can't go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But I failed to become a human, so I can't go to the place where Yukiji is, even if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That human girl, did you really like her that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,More than anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.45,0:06:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what price I would need to pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to be with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.38,0:06:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are a god as you say, will you look after me in my final moments?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a pitiful child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.60,0:06:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But you don't have to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me lend you a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.22,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The weakened you doesn't know how to heal yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time the sun rises and sets, the pain in your heart will slowly heal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll slowly forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the power of the oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:07:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I stopped the curse by making him forget,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.03,0:07:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe still remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,About Yukiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The curse, this time, will definitely end up killing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.59,0:07:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If him remembering it might lead to his death, we just have to make him forget once again, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.38,0:07:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:21.22,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he forgets about Yukiji-san, he'll be saved, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.45,0:07:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-san, please return it-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.32,0:07:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe doesn't want you to see his troubled self.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he cares for you more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you consider his feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.62,0:07:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a lie! Didn't you say earlier, that even I could save Tomoe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.80,0:07:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted him to bond with humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.92,0:07:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tomoe still doesn't want anything to do with humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He has no interest in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still attached to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't even take my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's always looking down on humans and saying harsh things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.06,0:08:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I love such a Tomoe, a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a lie, Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he fell in love with a human, my spell was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he loves you, his memories of Yukiji returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he adores you, my spell was broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.52,0:08:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.88,0:08:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Tomoe came to love a human once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:08:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:08:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.58,0:09:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.92,0:09:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, since I've come back, you don't have to hold back on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Nanami-san is this shrine's god right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sake is really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.47,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-kun is on the verge of death! Is this any time to enjoy drinking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:23.49,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you! Please help Tomoe-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I too want to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I desperately pondered over it for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.85,0:09:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.58,0:09:38.04,Sign,,0,0,0,,Pissed
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You, too, should do what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even Mikage-san can remove the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected, it definitely suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When he gave me this hairpin in autumn, he was still healthy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.22,0:10:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That time's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.56,0:10:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...the Tomoe from that time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.53,0:10:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...That time's...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...That time's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-sama, please don't blame yourself like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There are things that can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:53.88,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.81,0:10:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! The Tomoe from that time! The Tomoe from long ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.11,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nanami-sama!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,For Tomoe-kun's sake... for Nanami-chan's sake... something I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can travel to the past using the time travelling censer and prevent him from making the contract,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,then Tomoe won't be killed. The contract will become invalid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.70,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely save Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.89,0:11:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami-sama!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.50,0:11:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Mikage-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.10,0:11:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the past and stop Tomoe's contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use Mizuki's time travelling censer,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.87,0:11:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a moment, Nanami-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't simply go and change the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.47,0:11:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The flow of time is a domain that even the gods must not meddle with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.50,0:11:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the past exists, the present does too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:12:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If the contract had never existed, Tomoe might never have come to this shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, you might be throwing away the future of you meeting Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Meeting Tomoe would not exist...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But... even then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better than him dying like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.33,0:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to save him!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.60,0:12:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, there still are 6 days, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.63,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.24,0:12:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki, please take out the time travelling censer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.60,0:12:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki-dono, with a sombre look on his face, took the censer and went somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.80,0:12:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking the censer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.29,0:13:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Tomoe-kun hadn't come,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'd still be at the Yonomori shrine, looking at the plum tree, sitting alone like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.56,0:13:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lonely, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.14,0:13:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even then, if it saves Tomoe-kun, if it makes Nanami-chan smile,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.88,0:13:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll carry you to the past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mizuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.80,0:13:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandoning Mizuki, I could never do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.23,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That which must not change, is not the past, but the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,For that sake, I'll go back to the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The fallen god who made the contract with Tomoe,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,would definitely know of a way to undo the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll meet the fallen god and bring the key to break the curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Nanami-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.88,0:14:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,500 years ago is too different from today's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.88,0:14:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you sense even the slightest danger, please return back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an absolute promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.16,0:14:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.76,0:14:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The past won't change,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}because our fates are all connected by it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.68,0:14:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You finally did it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Realizing it by yourself is what was important.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.04,0:14:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's meet again later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aota's army has a 1000 men, ours has 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.81,0:15:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us settle this before morning, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Our army at Karakuri Castle is equipped and our opponent is not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Crush the rabble in one go-!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.52,0:15:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,MY LORD!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've kept you all waiting, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I, Akura-ou-sama, will be your army's general.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.81,0:15:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A DEMON!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You fiend! How dare you do that to our lord!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.34,0:15:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Looks amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Those sticks sure are extremely loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.90,0:15:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I love loud things a lot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Monster! Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.26,0:16:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!? Don't interfere with my game of siege.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Akura-ou, your body might be immortal,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.77,0:16:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but that kimono isn't! Return my haori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.82,0:16:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked fit for a lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a hole in it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going!? Stay close by!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving for 2/3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Till then, you'd better finish your foolish game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tch, such an unsociable guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the sake of saving Tomoe, I came to the past, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...currently, I am...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...all tied up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like an ordinary girl, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,there are pretty looking *youkai too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,50)}*Note: youkai=supernatural beings
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.69,0:16:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you, I'm not a youkai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an underling of that youkai named Tomoe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That face says you know him, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is definitely a youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The men of this village were all informed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Through a dazzling light in a dream, the voice of god was heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To regain our peaceful lives from before, we must exterminate youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we start with the leader,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the fox youkai, Tomoe that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe is!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This means that god is on mankind's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So then, tell me where the fox's lair is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe is being targeted by a god...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.15,0:17:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want to be burned, cough up the location of the fox's lair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, aren't you all loud during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.17,0:17:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing with a lone girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.22,0:18:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The beautiful person... I'd seen that time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.29,0:18:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.40,0:18:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This person is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Yukiji-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business! Women shouldn't enter the jail house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl's a woman too, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.67,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, this one's a youkai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.84,0:18:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's wrong!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a youkai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What hate-filled eyes...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.59,0:18:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This person... despises youkai!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.74,0:18:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught the wrong one. Untie her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.14,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,WHAT!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This one knows about that youkai named Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.93,0:18:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you lot are announcing it all over the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.65,0:19:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were called by the voice of the god, how about hurrying to get the youkai's head?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a woman! What's with that tone of speaking!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! For taking birth from just a woman's womb, you, too, shouldn't be talking that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You there, Sukeroku, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you help me untie that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.49,0:19:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Yukiji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.73,0:19:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Suke!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys have never really seen a youkai before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not from this village, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This person is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.05,0:19:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...Yukiji-san.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person whom Tomoe loves enough to even die for.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.30,0:19:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's frustrating, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...I can understand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they hit you on the face?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's a mystery...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.96,0:20:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.54,0:20:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that this girl seems so dear to me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.52,0:20:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cool down your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-sama~!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How dull.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukune's mind is always filled with thoughts about Tomoe-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's for your sake, I don't mind giving up my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.98,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You... smell of another man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.64,0:20:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No way~! Tomoe-sama~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How boring...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.99,0:21:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...both this woman and this place.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.01,0:21:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.31,0:21:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.27,0:21:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...that one's good enough.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.72,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that fox Tomoe, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.26,0:21:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ikusagami Takehaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.05,0:21:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come on orders from Izumo,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to eradicate all the youkai that disrupt the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're first, fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Tsukune? You can sacrifice yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.01,0:21:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll watch you, so go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You insolent fox!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,A god coming to such a place, just to kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.18,0:21:54.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wild fox, you'll suffer by my hands. You should feel honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.70,0:22:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.57,0:22:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a divine sword I borrowed from Ookuninushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.46,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ama no Hahakiri!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.03,0:22:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Die, fox!!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.92,0:22:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe-sama...!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, escape somewhere.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.70,0:22:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe-sama...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.81,0:22:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...you probably will...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.60,0:22:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...continue being alone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.26,0:22:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...without ever loving anyone, won't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.22,0:22:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ran away to the human world, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that wound will undoubtedly cease his movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.96,0:22:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already warned the humans of that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.07,0:22:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Fox, it's also fine if you are tormented to death, by those hot-blooded humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.48,0:22:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, damn it!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.26,0:22:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To think I'd be this humiliated.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seems like I have to hide myself for a while.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blood...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this my blood?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.34,0:23:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm seeing it for the first time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No good..!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I... can't move anymore.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a fox youkai!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.00,0:23:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!!! Tomoe's here!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is he!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.89,0:23:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That was delicious! Thank you for the meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.74,0:23:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,3 days after arriving in the past, I finally got a chance to bathe and dine today.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.95,0:23:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.68,0:23:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to have been on a long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You can rest in my house as long as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.58,0:24:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.90,0:24:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,My kimono looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.73,0:24:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.56,0:24:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wear the clothes you wore before, you'll be accused again by the village men, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.96,0:24:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.84,0:24:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yukiji-san... is so kind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.24,0:24:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe too, surely, must have been touched by her kindness and fallen for her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.24,0:24:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Yukiji, it's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.10,0:24:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuuta? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.78,0:24:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The fox, that they were mentioning before, has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.59,0:24:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the village men are cornering him towards the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.74,0:24:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A fox youkai, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.19,0:24:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,A white fox that uses blue flames.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.70,0:24:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks human and seems to be wearing dark clothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.67,0:24:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems to have become very weak, so they can take him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.25,0:24:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All able men are going to the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.77,0:24:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe...It's Tomoe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.54,0:25:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The injured Tomoe-kun who collapsed by the riverside was saved by Yukiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.28,0:25:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems, that's how their relationship started.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.26,0:25:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A youkai slaughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.06,0:25:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.42,0:25:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall have a feast tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.05,0:25:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.74,0:25:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to join in. You must be tired, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.10,0:25:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you going? To where Tomoe is?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.30,0:25:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.41,0:25:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.58,0:25:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Tomoe's injured...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.35,0:25:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to see a youkai's face.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.95,0:25:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Youkai are better off dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.54,0:25:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh!?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.43,0:25:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Isn't Yukiji-san going to go rescue Tomoe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.67,0:25:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got him! We've got the fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.68,0:25:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tomoe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.23,0:25:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.65,0:25:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My lady, Nanami went towards the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.78,0:25:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll follow her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.34,0:25:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.92,0:25:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't leave her be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.57,0:25:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because she somehow resembles Lady Yukiji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.60,0:25:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.44,0:26:01.84,overlap dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is the fox you caught, Sukeroku!?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.84,0:26:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.91,0:26:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If we take this as a hostage, he'll come out, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.30,0:26:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body won't listen to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.34,0:26:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If they hit me with their filthy hoes and sickles...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.88,0:26:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...someone like me... in a place like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.96,0:26:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...in such a place...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.92,0:26:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...will die, is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.88,0:26:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A human's coming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.32,0:26:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would a child's appearance...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.24,0:26:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...disguise me enough?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.94,0:26:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might still be discovered because of this wound.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.15,0:26:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's going dark before my eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.01,0:26:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomoe!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.02,0:26:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In an instant, my heart was stolen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.27,0:27:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, it's those eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.17,0:27:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's alright now, Tomoe.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.88,0:27:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the first woman I have wanted to claim as my own.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.84,0:27:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the matter with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.89,0:27:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that foxes can change form.\NPerhaps that child is the fox youkai that's been hunted right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.14,0:27:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's... a child I know...\N Please help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.16,0:28:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami, how about you stop hiding and show your face?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.67,0:28:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must not get in the way of Tomoe and Yukiji-san's relationship of the past.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.58,0:28:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body is burning.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.92,0:28:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where is this place?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.03,0:28:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.87,0:28:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are your favorite rice cakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.95,0:28:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who wants cakes?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.68,0:28:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is she?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.90,0:28:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're being overly familiar.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.31,0:28:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah, it's you again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.63,0:28:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When I return to my original form,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.24,0:28:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}so then,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.22,0:28:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what shall I do to you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.23,0:29:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(580,120)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.74,0:28:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,She cannot meddle with the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.72,0:29:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami continues to care for Tomoe from the shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.43,0:29:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet Tomoe decides to kill Nanami with his own hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.24,0:29:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanami's body has once again reached its limit for time traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.70,0:29:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, The Fox Falls in Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.49,0:29:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where will their fate take them?
